text: Georgia-Anastasia Tembou (born 23 April 1980) is a Greek gymnast. She competed in six events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Greek female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Greece Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Thessaloniki
